1. *Stoji* tu već pola sata. (He's been standing here for half an hour.)
2. Ne znam da li ću *stojati* dovoljno dugo. (I don't know if I'll be able to stand for long enough.)
3. *Stojim* usred sobe. (I'm standing in the middle of the room.)
4. Ne mogu da verujem da si *stojala* pored njega. (I can't believe that you were standing next to him.)
5. On je *stao* na vrh brda. (He stood on top of the hill.)
6. Budi spreman da *staneš* iza mene. (Be ready to stand behind me.)